title: Ingves and Jansson taking part in IMF Annual Meeting (Sveriges Riksbank)
text: ( Source : Sveriges Riksbank ) Date08/10/ 2015 The annual meetings of the International Monetary Fund ( IMF ) and the World Bank will take place in Lima on 9-10 October. The Swedish delegation will include Governor Stefan Ingves , Deputy Governor
